Package jalse.entities.methods

This package provides EntityMethod that are mapped to actual methods called on Entity (mapped by EntityFunctionResolver using the relevant EntityMethodFunction).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EntityMethod
    This is used to map from a Method called on an Entity type to a desired function.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultMethod
    This is used for mapping default methods.
    GetAttributeMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to: * AttributeContainer.getOptAttribute(String, AttributeType) AttributeContainer.getAttribute(String, AttributeType)
    GetEntitiesMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to: EntityContainer.getEntities() EntityContainer.getEntitiesOfType(Class) EntityContainer.getEntitiesAsType(Class)
    GetEntityMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to: EntityContainer.getEntityAsType(UUID, Class) EntityContainer.getOptEntityAsType(UUID, Class)
    KillEntitiesMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to EntityContainer.killEntities().
    KillEntityMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to EntityContainer.killEntity(UUID).
    MarkAsTypeMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to Entity.markAsType(Class).
    NewEntityMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to: EntityContainer.newEntity() EntityContainer.newEntity(UUID) EntityContainer.newEntity(Class) EntityContainer.newEntity(AttributeContainer) EntityContainer.newEntity(UUID, Class) EntityContainer.newEntity(UUID, AttributeContainer) EntityContainer.newEntity(Class, AttributeContainer) EntityContainer.newEntity(UUID, Class, AttributeContainer)
    ScheduleForActorMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to ActionScheduler.scheduleForActor(Action, long, long, TimeUnit).
    SetAttributeMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to: AttributeContainer.setOptAttribute(String, AttributeType, Object) AttributeContainer.setAttribute(String, AttributeType, Object) AttributeContainer.removeOptAttribute(String, AttributeType) AttributeContainer.removeAttribute(String, AttributeType)
    StreamEntitiesMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to: EntityContainer.streamEntities() EntityContainer.streamEntitiesOfType(Class) EntityContainer.streamEntitiesAsType(Class)
    UnmarkAsTypeMethod
    This is used for mapping calls to Entity.unmarkAsType(Class).
